    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. It runs smoothly and reliably, with all major mechanical systems, including the engine and transmission, performing exactly as they should. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips and light surface scratches, the overall paint and body are in great shape. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only minimal wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
