    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride that\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a solid value! While it shows some honest wear from its years of service, it remains a reliable performer that gets the job done every day. It\u2019s a great choice for anyone who appreciates a functional vehicle with plenty of life left and a bit of character. This is your chance to own a steady companion at a price that makes sense!",
